<div id="Idea_3939"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3939-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3939">Create an after hours clinic (5p-8a) adjacent to hospitals&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/8435-4049">sabude1</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">2 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">My goal is to decrease wait time and cost when needing a doctor after hours. The idea is to have an adjacent clinic to the emergency room at hospitals that are staffed to assess, handle, and treat patients as if they were visiting their doctors office (hopefully better). If the patients' need hospitalization then they can have an automatic referral to the emergency room right across the hall for the emergency physician to sign them in. </div>
