<div id="Idea_3724"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3724-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3724">Contact Info or Sending Private Messages Needed&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/5117-4049">Rob  Wheeler</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">3 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">There are a number of people that had really great ideas that I have wanted to contact. It would be great if you could add an option for people to be able to contact each other - either a way to send private messages or to list email addresses in their profiles or something. <br/><br/>Rob Wheeler</div>
