<div id="Idea_3723"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaTitle">
<a href="/akira/dtd/3723-4049"><span id="IdeaTitle_3723">Separate out gambling out of Investments&nbsp;</span></a>
</div>
<table width=@%">  <tr>    <td valign="top"><div id="IdeaScale_IdeaSubTitle"><b><a href="http://opengov.ideascale.com/akira/pmd/7305-4049">Joseph Rizzi</a></b> <span class="IdeaScale_SecondaryText">3 days ago</span></div></td>    <td align="right" valign="top"></td>  </tr></table>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaContent">The stock market and investments have gotten away from actually being investments.  Lets get the gambling in it own market or back in Vagas.<br/><br/>Oil should be traded by only those that are going to use it.</div>
<div id="IdeaScale_IdeaFooter"><span style="border-right: 1px solid silver; margin:0 10px 0 0; padding: 0 5px 0 0; color: #666;"><a id="DiscussionTopic_3723" href="javascript:ajaxLink('DiscussionTopicComment_3723', '/akira/discussion.do?mode=comment&dbid=2255&topicID=3723')">Comments (0)</a></span><span id="DiscussionTopicTag_3723"><a href="/akira/ideafactory.do?discussionID=2255">Uncategorized</a></span></div><div style="margin-top:3px;" id="DiscussionTopicComment_3723"></div>
